data.description: This 4-bed plus den, 2.5 bath single story home sits on the 4th hole of the Duke golf course with an extended 3 car garage. This hacienda home features 2x6 construction, RV gate, travertine and wood look tile, surround sound, tons of can lighting and shutters throughout.  The Kitchen is a chef's dream, with gorgeous white and grey cabinetry, SS appliances, gas range, granite counters, and an island with breakfast bar. The huge master suite offers backyard access and a resort style bathroom with his/her sinks,  soaking tub, tiled walk in shower and a walk-in closet WITH laundry.  The Backyard is an oasis, featuring a covered patio, private putting green, a refreshing pool for summer with heater for cooler months and breathtaking views. This is a rare opportunity to own a slice of paradise
